Package com.ikarus.solartaxi.celestialbodies

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CelestialBody
    This class represents a CelestialBody, either a 'Sun' or a 'Planet' object.
    Planet
    Represents a Planet object with a center, a radius and a gravitation.
    Sun
    Represents a Sun object with a center, a radius, a gravitation value and a value for emmitted energy.
